text:
Heh, this is amazing...! I didn't expect to find
such a wide selection of retro games.

Oh, this puzzle game...
I've played it before.

Tenka, know this one too...!
We had it at home...!

Haha, sounds good!
Let's do it!
Hmm, I didn't stand a chance at all...

No, I'm the one who should apologize
for losing track of time and getting carried away...

But let's have a rematch sometime, Tenka.
I won't lose next time!
